nfidential Information of Disclosing Party (including any copies thereof) or certify the destruction thereof.3. All right title and interest in and to the Confidential Information shall remain with Disclosing Party or its licensors. Nothing in this Agreement is intended to grant any rights to Recipient under any patents, copyrights, trademarks, or trade secrets of Disclosing Party.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2726, "end_char_idx": 3195, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "95485ff1-69cc-4c16-81e4-e26cf84b7c7d": {"__data__": {"id_": "95485ff1-69cc-4c16-81e4-e26cf84b7c7d", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "c268e2f3-8d98-4da7-befe-b841022c5f64", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "66342d25c839fec2a19061a16f3916c9f0a149edb002efd8a08bed8e0445c777", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "237805f0-d597-49c8-8429-29b8ccd4bbc8", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "17964b78e87d0c26477ebbcf78c5d14349acc9fbf2e64587f6a3224af5608656", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "02f46868-0e13-4758-8513-2e2806b1feec", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "d1aa0a94885a522985389ed7c6fb2b7aadc09e4a9535ddcf3b3c1bc8ea7b6842", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "ALL CONFIDENTIAL INFORMATION IS PROVIDED \"AS IS\".\n\n THE DISCLOSING PARTY MAKES NO WARRANTIES, EXPRESS, IMPLIED OR OTHERWISE, REGARDING NON-INFRINGEMENT OF THIRD PARTY RIGHTS OR ITS ACCURACY, COMPLETENESS OR PERFORMANCE.4.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3196, "end_char_idx": 3417, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "02f46868-0e13-4758-8513-2e2806b1feec": {"__data__": {"id_": "02f46868-0e13-4758-8513-2e2806b1f